source.name: United States Army Affirmative Claims Annual Recoveries
source.description: Aggregation of the US Army Affirmative Claims Recoveries for selected Fiscal Years.  These amounts, in US dollars, is money recovered from 3rd parties and returned to Army and other services Military Treatment Facilities (MTF's) or to TRICARE.
